### Is this a regression?

- [X] Yes, this behavior used to work in the previous version

### The previous version in which this bug was not present was

14

### Description

I have migrated angular from ver 14 to 15, In angular ver 14 all things are working good, after migrating to angular material 15 buttons are not picking the custom text color and background color. 

**button theme:**
@use '../_variables' as vars;

@mixin theme() {
	.blue-button {
		background-color: vars.$primary-default;
		color: white;
	}
}

**this class is overriding the font-color of the button :**
mat-mdc-button:not(:disabled) {
    color: var(--mdc-text-button-label-text-color, inherit);
}

**this class is overriding my background color:**
.mdc-button {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
}

**html file implementation of button:**
<button
	mat-button
	class="blue-button">
	Test
</button>

